<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4651954>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Pardosa pseudomixta sp. nov. (A–C,E,F) and Pardosa mixta (D,G,H). (A) Female, dorsal; (B) male, frontal; (C,D) male, lateral; (E,G), male leg I, prolateral; (F,H) male leg I, retrolateral. Arrows indicate differences in the coloration of the prosoma (light marginal band) and legs in males. Analogous figures have the same magnification." ;
