<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4651958>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Males of Pardosa pseudomixta sp. nov. (A,B,F–J) and Pardosa mixta (C–E). (A,C) leg I, prolateral; (B,D) metatarsus I, prolateral; (E,F,I) palp ventral; (G) palp retrolateral; (H) palp from above; (J) fine pore on metatarsus I (arrowed). Arrows indicate differences in the setae arrangement on the metatarsi between both species and fine pore. Scale 0.1 mm if not otherwise indicated." ;
